PrecisAmendments to the HIV-INFECTED PERSONS AND THALIDOMIDE VICTIMS ASSISTANCE ORDER which extend the deadline for HIV applications to March 31, 1994, and authorize the Minister to accept an application after that date if satisfied that an applicant was unable to submit one before that date because of circumstances beyond their control.
